Australian Carboniferous species. 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686196B3FFCB784F1FB26F736" authority="Yoo, 1994" authorityName="Yoo" authorityYear="1994" box="[879,1212,2181,2221]" class="Gastropoda" family="Platyceratidae" genus="Platyschisma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Euomphalina" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="lingua" status="n.sp.">
<emphasis id="B936EAC786196B3FFCB784F1FB26F736" box="[879,1212,2181,2221]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">Platyschisma lingua</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A20557BC86196B3FFF3E84C0FEADF740" box="[230,311,2228,2267]" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" rank="species">n.sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, from 'Rangari'; 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686196B3FFD5D84C0FC7AF740" authority="Yoo, 1994" authorityName="Yoo" authorityYear="1994" box="[645,992,2228,2267]" class="Gastropoda" family="Platyceratidae" genus="Platyschisma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Euomphalina" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="vitrea" status="n.sp.">
<emphasis id="B936EAC786196B3FFD5D84C0FC7AF740" box="[645,992,2228,2267]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">Platyschisma vitrea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A20557BC86196B3FFC2184C0FBD0F740" box="[1017,1098,2228,2267]" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" rank="species">n.sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, from 'Marohn'.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C358655E86196B3FFECE8564FD82F54F" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BFD36D586196B3FFECE8564FD82F54F" blockId="11.[228,1215,2181,2772]" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">
Remarks. The Early Permian species 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686196B3FFC038564FD76F6FF" authority="Mitchell (1922)" authorityName="Mitchell" authorityYear="1922" class="Gastropoda" family="Platyceratidae" genus="Platyschisma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Euomphalina" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="allandalensis">
<emphasis id="B936EAC786196B3FFC038564FE5FF6FF" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">Platyschisma allandalensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFD34B2486196B3FFE038549FD76F6FF" author="Mitchell, J." box="[475,748,2365,2404]" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" pagination="278" refId="ref26788" refString="Mitchell, J., 1922. A new gastropod (Fam. Euomphalidae) from the lower marine series of New South Wales. Linnean Society of New South Wales Proceedings 47: 278." type="journal article" year="1922">Mitchell (1922)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and the form referred to 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686196B3FFF3C8518FD7DF608" authority="Sowerby" authorityName="Sowerby" box="[228,743,2412,2451]" class="Gastropoda" family="Platyceratidae" genus="Platyschisma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Euomphalina" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="oculus">
<emphasis id="B936EAC786196B3FFF3C8518FDDBF608" box="[228,577,2412,2451]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">Platyschisma oculus</emphasis>
Sowerby
</taxonomicName>
by de 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD34B2486196B3FFCB18518FBE2F608" author="Koninck, L. G. de" box="[873,1144,2412,2451]" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" pagination="1 - 294" refId="ref26401" refString="Koninck, L. G. de, 1876. Recherches sur 1 es Fossiles Paleozoiques de da Nouvelle Galles du Sud (Australia). Mem. Soc. Roy. Sci. Liege. 2, 6. (Translated, 1898, as: Descriptions of the Palaeozoic fossils of New South Wales (Australia). Geological Survey of New South Wales (Palaeontology) 6: 1 - 294." type="journal article" year="1876">Koninck (1876)</bibRefCitation>
are large in size. The width of 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686196B3FFD1585EEFC79F65A" authorityName="Mitchell" authorityYear="1922" box="[717,995,2458,2497]" class="Gastropoda" family="Platyceratidae" genus="Platyschisma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Euomphalina" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="allandalensis">
<emphasis id="B936EAC786196B3FFD1585EEFC79F65A" box="[717,995,2458,2497]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">P. allandalensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is lO 
<quantity id="4CBA9B3086196B3FFB9585EEFB2FF65A" box="[1101,1205,2458,2497]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" unit="mm" value="5.0">5 mm</quantity>
. The original figures of 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686196B3FFD5585BCFC3FF674" authorityName="Mitchell" authorityYear="1922" box="[653,933,2504,2543]" class="Gastropoda" family="Platyceratidae" genus="Platyschisma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Euomphalina" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="allandalensis">
<emphasis id="B936EAC786196B3FFD5585BCFC3FF674" box="[653,933,2504,2543]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">P. allandalensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
does not show the detail of the shell, and its exact locality is not known. Comparison of 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686196B3FFD4D8650FC2AF5D0" authorityName="Mitchell" authorityYear="1922" box="[661,944,2596,2635]" class="Gastropoda" family="Platyceratidae" genus="Platyschisma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Euomphalina" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="allandalensis">
<emphasis id="B936EAC786196B3FFD4D8650FC2AF5D0" box="[661,944,2596,2635]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">P. allandalensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with the 
<typeStatus id="54F9887786196B3FFBAC8650FB26F5D0" box="[1140,1212,2596,2635]" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">type</typeStatus>
species, 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686196B3FFE558626FB9BF5E2" authority="Sowerby" authorityName="Sowerby" box="[397,1025,2642,2681]" class="Gastropoda" family="Platyceratidae" genus="Platyschisma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Euomphalina" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="helicoides">
<emphasis id="B936EAC786196B3FFE558626FCD8F5E2" box="[397,834,2642,2681]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">Platyschisma helicoides</emphasis>
Sowerby
</taxonomicName>
, suggests that 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686196B3FFEE486F4FDCDF53C" authorityName="Mitchell" authorityYear="1922" box="[316,599,2688,2727]" class="Gastropoda" family="Platyceratidae" genus="Platyschisma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Euomphalina" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="allandalensis">
<emphasis id="B936EAC786196B3FFEE486F4FDCDF53C" box="[316,599,2688,2727]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">P. allandalensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is better referred to 
<taxonomicName id="4C424D5686196B3FFC2E86F4FB1AF53C" authorityName="Etheridge" authorityYear="1902" box="[1014,1152,2688,2727]" class="Gastropoda" family="Platyceratidae" genus="Keeneia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Euomphalina" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B936EAC786196B3FFC2E86F4FB1AF53C" box="[1014,1152,2688,2727]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="74">Keeneia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
of 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD34B2486196B3FFF3C86D9FD89F54F" author="Etheridge, R. Jr." box="[228,531,2733,2772]" pageId="11" pageNumber="74" pagination="195 - 200" refId="ref25406" refString="Etheridge, R. Jr., 1902. A new Permo-Carboniferous genus (Keeneia). Records of the Australian Museum IV, 5: 195 - 200." type="journal article" year="1902">Etheridge (1902)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
